DISCLAIMER:

This device is provided for educational and recreational use only. It is NOT
intended for professional navigation, search and rescue operations, life-safety
applications, or any mission-critical use.

Users must:
- Always carry proper maps, compass, and emergency equipment
- Know how to use traditional navigation methods
- Plan routes appropriately
- Inform others of hiking plans
- Be prepared for device failure

The creators and contributors assume no liability for:
- Device malfunctions or failures
- Inaccurate navigation information
- Personal injury or property damage
- Getting lost or stranded
- Any other consequences of device use

GPS and compass readings can be affected by terrain, weather, interference,
and hardware limitations. Users assume all risk when using this device.

ALWAYS prioritize safety and proper outdoor skills over reliance on any
electronic device.
